OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry night
OL,6,Fwith late sunshine then clear spells,
OL,7,Fthough higher cloud increasing
OL,8,Fovernight. Winds increasing to a fresh
OL,9,Fsoutheasterly across the coasts
OL,10,Ftowards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA dry morning with hazy
OL,13,Fsunshine. Cloud increasing during the
OL,14,Fafternoon to bring some patchy light
OL,15,Frain from late evening. East to
OL,16,Fsoutheast breezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
