OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FUnsettled with a series of rain bands
OL,7,Fcrossing from the west. However, with
OL,8,Fwinds staying southwesterly
OL,9,Ftemperatures a little up on the
OL,10,Fseasonal averages.
